title: Lunchbox Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Located in a small drive-through stand, this place is open to accommodate special requests. Sandwiches are sold by the half (palm of the hand sized), and soups are sold in cups. Has a sandwich with avocado, hummus, sprouts, and tomato on your choice of bread; a vegetarian sandwich with cream cheese; and soup of the day is sometimes vegan.
